description: This file declares exported API functions for the Beep Client Session Object, including creation, removal, and initialization routines. It serves as an interface specification for other components to interact with the Beep Client Session functionality.

methods.name: BeepCreateClientSession
methods.description: Creates and initializes a new Beep Client Session object with given context handles.

methods.name: BeepCsoCreate
methods.description: Creates a new Beep Client Session Object with provided context handles.

methods.name: BeepCsoRemove
methods.description: Removes and deallocates the specified Beep Client Session Object.

methods.name: BeepCsoEnrollObjects
methods.description: Enrolls and sets up necessary objects within the Beep Client Session Object.

methods.name: BeepCsoInitialize
methods.description: Initializes the Beep Client Session Object.
